p.annot: Scans der OA aus dem Beethovenhaus: aus Finale generierte MusicXML-Daten die in MEI konvertiert (MusicXMLToMEI-xslt) wurden
Der Instrumentenvorsatz und dessen Abkürzungen von der NGA übernommen.

changeDesc.p: Transcoded from a MusicXML version 3.0 file using an XSLT stylesheet (musicxml2mei v. 3.0).
Converted to version 3.0.0 using mei21To30.xsl, version 1.0 beta
Converted to MEI version 4.0.0 using mei30To40.xsl, version 1.0 beta
genereted new uuids for the whole file to ensure data consistency; utilizing clean.xml-id.xsl

Deleted mei:sb-elements and mei:pb-elements, got rid of rend-elements but keep its contents, renamed mSpace-elements to mRest-elements, moved accid-attributes from accid-elements to note-elements, moved artic-attributes from artic-elements to note-elements; utilizing dataCleanUp.xsl
harmonize tstamp/tstamp2 and startid/endid for controlenvents based on the bw_module2_works.odd to ensure data consistency; utilizing controlevent.fixer.xsl
convert tupletSpans to tuplets; utilizing convert.tupletSpan.xsl
convert fermata attributes to elements; utilizing convert.fermata2elem.xsl
convert tie attributes to elements, utilizing convert.tie2elem.xsl
corrected "Dreistimmiger Chor" to "dreistimmiger Chor"
corrections part 1 (Clarinetto I in B), part 2 (Clarinetto II in B), part 3 (Fagotto I), part 4 (Fagotto II) according to paper-proofreading.
corrections part 5 (Corni I in B), part 6 (Corni II in B), part 7 (Sologesang I), part 8 (Sologesang II) and part 9 (dreistimmiger Chor) according to paper-proofreading.
minor corrections. Key-Change-Test.
All Clef-Changes (Fg I and II) which where encoded as separate staffDefs changed to clef-changes within the measures.
second corrections: part 1.
second corrections: part 2.
second corrections: part 3.
second corrections: part 4.
second corrections: part 5 and 6.
second corrections: part 7, 8 and 9.
corrected some dynam-tsamps and commented some OA-mistakes.
converted crescendo-dirs to dynam-elements and set extender-attributes with tstamp2s.
Songtextstandardization part 7.
Songtextstandardization part 8.
Songtextstandardization part 9.
